Dialogue: 2,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.06,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}2014年 在那个神奇的山东招远市
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.75,0:13:30.06,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In 2014, in Zhao Yun City, China, 
Dialogue: 2,0:13:30.36,0:13:35.17,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一家麦当劳成为了被监控拍下的top5哈人犯罪现场之一
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.36,0:13:35.17,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the McDonald's became the scene of one of the most disturbing crimes caught on surveillance.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.39,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一场发生在家庭、孩子和顾客面前的血腥谋杀
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.20,0:13:40.39,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}A murder carried out in front of families, children, and customers.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而凶手们 则相信自己正在对抗“恶灵”
Dialogue: 1,0:13:41.56,0:13:45.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}All by a group who believed they were fighting evil spirits.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.00,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是5月28日 一个五指不见伸手的夜晚
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.84,0:13:51.00,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It was the evening of May 28th.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:51.46,0:13:57.05,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}37岁的吴硕艳是在一位在附近一家服装店工作的销售员
Dialogue: 1,0:13:51.46,0:13:57.05,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Wu Zhao Yun, 37 years old, a salesperson who worked at a nearby clothing store.
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.03,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经下班的她在麦当劳等着家人们的到来
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.06,0:14:02.03,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}After work, she was waiting at a McDonald's for her family to arrive.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:04.43,0:14:10.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}大约晚上9点 六个人走了进来 包括五名成年人和一个少年
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.43,0:14:10.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Around 9 pm, a group of six people entered, a mix of adults, and even one teenager.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.44,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他们不是来点餐的 
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.35,0:14:13.44,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But they weren't there to order food.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:14.07,0:14:19.96,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们是来传教的
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.07,0:14:19.96,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Instead, they started preaching to customers, telling them about their religious beliefs.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.43,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但这还没完 
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.43,0:14:23.43,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But it didn't just stop there.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:23.75,0:14:29.83,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们还要所有人的手机号码 声称他们将来还会联系
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.75,0:14:29.83,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It began demanding everyone's cell phone numbers, claiming they needed them to future contact.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:34.52,0:14:40.36,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而当吴数次拒绝他们时 他们就开始向她发起攻击
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.52,0:14:40.36,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And when Wu refused, not once, but twice, they turned on her.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.11,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这群人喊道 她是个恶魔
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.68,0:14:43.11,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The group shouted that she was an evil spirit.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:43.72,0:14:47.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}然后他们就开始在餐厅里所有人的面前攻击她
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.72,0:14:47.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And then, in front of the entire restaurant, they began attacking her.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.20,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们使用的武器包括椅子、拖把和他们的脚
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.04,0:14:50.20,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Chairs, mops, and their feet.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.66,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这些动作毫不留情
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.52,0:14:52.66,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The beating was merciless.
Dialogue: 2,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.65,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而任何试图干预的人则都受到了同样的威胁
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.84,0:14:58.65,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And anyone who tried to intervene was threatened with the same fate.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.46,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而监控拍下了这一切
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.15,0:15:03.46,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and the CCTV cameras recorded everything.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:05.07,0:15:10.37,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}顾客们惊恐地不断后退 而吴则在众目睽睽之下被殴打致死
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.07,0:15:10.37,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Customers backed away in fear as Wu was beaten to death and in full public view.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.22,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}当警察到达时 他们逮捕了六名袭击者
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.22,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}When police finally arrived, they arrested all six attackers.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:20.56,0:15:27.94,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}中国政府的通报称 凶手是“全能神”教会的成员
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.56,0:15:27.94,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Chinese government quickly reported that the killers were members of the Eastern Lightning cult.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是一个备受争议的、根据基督教瞎编的教派
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a controversial Christian-inspired sect.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:30.58,0:15:36.58,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该教派成立于1990年代 长期以来被国家列入邪教的清单
Dialogue: 1,0:15:30.58,0:15:36.58,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Found in the 1990s, which has been long accused by the state of being a dangerous cult.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:37.61,0:15:44.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}全能神教会 是一个受基督教启发的团体 于1990年代在中国成立
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.61,0:15:44.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Eastern Lightning, or the Church of Almighty God, is a Christian-inspired group founded in China in the 1990s.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.48,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}据该团体的教典称 基督已经回归
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.37,0:15:48.48,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}According to the group, Christ is returned, 
Dialogue: 2,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.85,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但祂以一位中国女性的形式出现 而他们的追随者必须接受他们的教义
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.85,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}but in the form of a Chinese woman, and their followers must embrace your teachings.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.49,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}政府将其列为邪教
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.45,0:15:56.49,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the government labels this as an evil cult.
Dialogue: 2,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}关键是 这个教派早就不是第一次出来跳了
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.25,0:16:01.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the thing is, this cult isn't even new to controversy.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:02.56,0:16:11.77,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}多年来 当局指控“全能神”犯有强制改宗、财务剥削、家庭暴力和骚扰等罪行
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.79,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Over the years, authorities have accused Eastern Lightning of forced conversations, 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.79,0:16:11.77,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}financial exploitation, domestic abuse, and harassment.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:12.17,0:16:13.69,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}据报道 在一些农村地区
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.17,0:16:17.97,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In some rural areas, reports say they apply high-pressure tactics on families to join or donate.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:13.69,0:16:17.97,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们对家庭施加高压策略 要求他们加入或捐款
Dialogue: 2,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.69,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对于这次麦当劳杀人事件
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.45,0:16:21.69,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}In the context of the McDonald's killing, 
Dialogue: 2,0:16:21.69,0:16:28.51,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}官方声称那六名袭击者来自“全能神”内部的一个奇怪的分支
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.69,0:16:28.51,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}the official narrative claims that the six attackers came from a dissident or strange subgroup within Eastern Lightning.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}他们可能不受教会中央的管理
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.37,0:16:32.33,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Maybe not fully under the church's central control.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.73,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但他们的行为符合一些更激进的邪教信仰 比如将非信徒视为恶灵
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.82,0:16:38.73,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}But their actions align with some of the more radical cult beliefs, rejecting non-believers as evil spirits,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.93,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要求服从 如要求提供电话号码或联系方式
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.00,0:16:42.93,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)} demanding submission, as in phone numbers or contact,
Dialogue: 2,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.09,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有暴力地强制执行他们的教义
Dialogue: 1,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.09,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}and enforcing their doctrine violently.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.82,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}袭击者接受了审判 
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.42,0:16:53.82,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And the attackers were put on trial.
Dialogue: 2,0:16:54.06,0:16:59.41,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}录像、证人和供词等都是判死他们的铁证
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.06,0:16:59.41,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The footage, the witnesses, and the confessions all made it impossible to deny what happened.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.94,0:17:05.86,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}团体中的两人 包括主犯 被判处死刑 并于2015年执行
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.94,0:17:03.16,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Two of the group, including the ringleaders,
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.86,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Senten to death and executed in 2015.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.33,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}其他人则被判处长期监禁
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.16,0:17:09.33,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The others received long prison sentences.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:10.25,0:17:15.18,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}尘埃落定之后 这个案件成为了现代中国最臭名昭著的邪教犯罪
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:15.18,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And in the aftermath, the case became one of the most infamous cult crimes in modern China.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:16.25,0:17:21.32,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它还导致了突袭、大规模逮捕和铁拳
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.25,0:17:21.32,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It sparked raids, mass arrests, and a crackdown on the Church of Almighty God.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.72,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}招远麦当劳命案至今仍是一个沉痛的警示
Dialogue: 1,0:17:23.15,0:17:26.72,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}The Xiaoyan McDonald's murder remains a disturbing reminder 
Dialogue: 2,0:17:26.92,0:17:33.40,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它向我们展示了信仰是如何走向狂热 并最终在最寻常不过的地方演变为骇人的暴力的
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.92,0:17:33.40,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}of how belief, worked into fanaticism, and erupted into violence, in the most ordinary places. 
Dialogue: 2,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.56,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在这个案件中 监控捕捉到的不仅仅是图像
Dialogue: 1,0:17:34.70,0:17:37.56,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It's a case where surveillance didn't just capture an image.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:37.80,0:17:43.60,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它捕捉到的是一个意识形态 是一个模糊了信仰和妄想界限的信仰体系
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.80,0:17:43.60,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}It captured an entire ideology, a belief system that blurred the line between faith and delusion.
Dialogue: 2,0:17:45.40,0:17:53.95,Default,atg1,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}它还向世界展示了当一个团体认为自己的谋杀实为救赎时的恐怖
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.40,0:17:53.95,Default-L2,atg2,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}And it showed the world of how truly terrifying it is when a group convinces themselves that killing isn't murder, as salvation.